quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  53,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  53,1,Wannajmi izaa hawaa
  53,2,Maa dalla saahibukum wa maa ghawaa
  53,3,Wa maa yyantiqu 'anilhawaaa
  53,4,In huwa illaa Wahyuny yoohaa
  53,5,'Allamahoo shadeedul quwaa
  53,6,Zoo mirratin fastawaa
  53,7,Wa huwa bil ufuqil a'laa
  53,8,Summa danaa fatadalla
  53,9,Fakaana qaaba qawsaini aw adnaa
  53,10,Fa awhaaa ilaa 'abdihee maaa awhaa
  53,11,Maa kazabal fu'aadu maa ra aa
  53,12,Afatumaaroonahoo 'alaa maayaraa
  53,13,Wa laqad ra aahu nazlatan ukhraa
  53,14,'Inda sidratil muntaha
  53,15,'Indahaa jannatul maawaa
  53,16,Iz yaghshas sidrata maa yaghshaa
  53,17,Maa zaaghal basaru wa maa taghaa
  53,18,Laqad ra aa min aayaati Rabbihil kubraaa
  53,19,Afara'aytumul laata wal 'uzzaa
  53,20,Wa manaatas saalisatal ukhraa
  53,21,A-lakumuz zakaru wa lahul unsaa
  53,22,Tilka izan qismatun deezaa
  53,23,In hiya illaaa asmaaa'un sammaitumoohaaa antum wa aabaaa'ukum maaa anzalal laahu bihaa min sultaan; inyyattabi'oona illaz zanna wa maa tahwal anfusu wa laqad jaaa'ahum mir Rabbihimul hudaa
  53,24,Am lil insaani maa taman naa
  53,25,Falillaahil aakhiratu wal oolaa
  53,26,Wa kam mim malakin fissamaawaati laa tughnee shafaa'atuhum shai'an illaa mim ba'di anyyaazanal laahu limany yashaaa'u wa yardaa
  53,27,innal lazeena laa yu'minoona bil aakhirati la yusammoonal malaaa'ikata tasmiyatal unsaa
  53,28,Wa maa lahum bihee min 'ilmin iny yattabi'oona illaz zanna wa innaz zanna laa yughnee minal haqqi shai'aa
  53,29,Fa a'rid 'am man tawallaa 'an zikrinaa wa lam yurid illal hayaatad dunyaa
  53,30,Zalika mablaghuhum minal 'ilm; inna rabbaka huwa a'lamu biman dalla 'an sabee lihee wa huwa a'lamu bimanih tadaa
  53,31,Wa lillaahi maa fis samaawaati wa maa fil ardi liyajziyal lazeena asaaa'oo bimaa 'amiloo wa yajziyal lazeena ahsanoo bilhusnaa
  53,32,Allazeena yajtaniboona kabaaa'iral ismi walfawaa hisha illal lamam; inna rabbaka waasi'ul maghfirah; huwa a'lamu bikum iz ansha akum minal ardi wa iz antum ajinnatun fee butooni umma haatikum falaa tuzakkooo anfusakum huwa a'lamu bimanit taqaa
  53,33,Afara'ayatal lazee tawallaa
  53,34,Wa a'taa qaleelanw wa akdaa
  53,35,A'indahoo 'ilmul ghaibi fahuwa yaraa
  53,36,Am lam yunabbaa bimaa fee suhuhfi Moosa
  53,37,Wa Ibraaheemal lazee waffaaa
  53,38,Allaa taziru waaziratunw wizra ukhraa
  53,39,Wa al laisa lil insaani illaa maa sa'aa
  53,40,Wa anna sa'yahoo sawfa yuraa
  53,41,Summa yujzaahul jazaaa 'al awfaa
  53,42,Wa anna ilaa rabbikal muntahaa
  53,43,Wa annahoo huwa adhaka wa abkaa
  53,44,Wa annahoo huwa amaata wa ahyaa
  53,45,Wa annahoo khalaqaz zawjainiz zakara wal unsaa
  53,46,Min nutfatin izaa tumnaa
  53,47,Wa anna 'alaihin nash atal ukhraa
  53,48,Wa annahoo huwa aghnaa wa aqnaa
  53,49,Wa annahoo huwa rabbush shi'raa
  53,50,Wa annahooo ahlak a 'Aadanil oolaa
  53,51,Wa samooda famaaa abqaa
  53,52,Wa qawma Noohim min qablu innahum kaanoo hum azlama wa atghaa
  53,53,Wal mu'tafikata ahwaa
  53,54,Faghashshaahaa maa ghashshaa
  53,55,Fabi ayyi aalaaa'i Rabbika tatamaaraa
  53,56,Haazaa nazeerum minan nuzuril oolaa
  53,57,Azifatil laazifah
  53,58,Laisa lahaa min doonil laahi kaashifah
  53,59,Afamin hazal hadeesi ta'jaboon
  53,60,Wa tadhakoona wa laa tabkoon
  53,61,Wa antum saamidoon
  53,62,Fasjudoo lillaahi wa'budoo�(make sajda)
